result.name: Chiu Fook

reviews.text: Not bad but not really nice. Not crowded at lunchtime.

Got the seafood steam set, 388 per head, plus 20 for condiments, plus 10 percent service charge. We found the portions of the seafood to be small ( like small sized lobster , small sized crab), but at least it was fresh. The all you can eat order portion ... Was not that great, felt it was like leftover dim sum. Service was very mixed, they cooked your food on time, and some really try. But overall not much dicipline, wait staff were eating food blatantly from customer table who had left, and calling each over to try whatever they were having, loudly for us to hear clearly. Many were busy with phones. If there were more customers, don't know how they would cope, as food came very slowly ( and it doesn't need to be cooked ??). Not two stars only because the seafood was alright.
Good food with very good price.  There is no tea charge at the moment because the lift is under repair.
Very good value for money. But don't expect the service though.
Good seafood 🦞 at great value. But it’s quite shocking 😰to see them putting up chairs on table cloth with unused tableware 🍽🥣🥢near closing hour

result.name: 潮福龍蝦專門店

reviews.text: 晚飯小菜打邊爐同外面D酒樓ㄧ樣ㄧ般😰重點晚飯時間龍蝦長腳蟹有冇特價平買
昨晚晚飯叫食龍蝦 餐牌388元有相片為証 是一隻龍蝦的 說明足一斤四両送伊麵。伙記寫单介紹有套餐龍蝦加燒鵝一隻是398元寫明是2隻開边龍蝦有相片的。當落单時我特別說明要388元的一隻龍蝦。結果上菜時發現变了二隻小龍蝦。立刻追究伙記，他說没有一隻龍蝦的，現二隻小龍蝦是足一斤四両的。我反問謂何做菜時不先通知我是否接受。我覺得有被欺騙的成份，特此告訴各位食客關注！
呢間酒樓兩個收銀簡直不知所謂。似住自己做得耐。朝頭早人哋排隊畀錢，佢兩個仲喺度傾計仲慢慢嚟。佢個樣好似話之你死噉。妳以為自己係老闆咩，打份工喺度巴巴閉。真係不知所謂。

最近酒樓升降機维修要走樓梯, 特別免茶錢優惠。
午茶時段蝦餃竟然有$9.9 一籠四隻的優惠!
点心質素ok, 配合優惠值得光顧!
早茶一般，沒什麼特色，盅頭飯比較大少少，茶錢8元，一般都這價錢，點心不過不失。
